00:00:02.419 --> 00:00:08.419
Today is a great day of Navaratri,

00:00:10.062 --> 00:00:16.937
we are sitting on the cusp of the sixth and the seventh.

00:00:18.716 --> 00:00:25.605
Sixth and the seventh is the day when Mahasaraswati

00:00:26.665 --> 00:00:28.693
finished Her work

00:00:28.773 --> 00:00:34.242
and the incarnation of the Shakti itself started.

00:00:34.322 --> 00:00:40.876
So, at twelve o’clock today the
Devi takes the Shakti upon Herself.

00:00:40.956 --> 00:00:48.424
Of course, as you know that Mahakali and Mahasaraswati,

00:00:48.504 --> 00:01:00.504
both are the powers of Shri Sadashiva.

00:01:01.561 --> 00:01:09.785
Adi Shakti first formed Herself into Mahakali,

00:01:09.865 --> 00:01:14.919
which is the Power of Desire.

00:01:14.999 --> 00:01:18.982
But all these powers are nothing

00:01:19.062 --> 00:01:26.999
but the power of God’s love.

00:01:28.817 --> 00:01:36.280
So, in the series of this great love of God,

00:01:36.360 --> 00:01:41.918
Adi Shakti had to first become the Power of Desire.

00:01:41.998 --> 00:01:43.758
In the same way,

00:01:43.838 --> 00:01:48.471
Sahaja Yogis who are bestowed with this power of love

00:01:48.551 --> 00:01:53.551
have to have full desire in their heart.

00:01:55.607 --> 00:02:00.551
Desire to love.

00:02:02.087 --> 00:02:07.552
That desire is very different from

00:02:07.632 --> 00:02:12.988
the other kinds of human love we have known.

00:02:13.068 --> 00:02:21.524
In other kinds of human love,
when we have relations with others,

00:02:21.604 --> 00:02:24.945
we have expectations,

00:02:25.025 --> 00:02:29.471
and that’s why it is very disappointing.

00:02:29.551 --> 00:02:33.471
Our expectations always run higher

00:02:33.551 --> 00:02:39.248
than our understanding and realities.

00:02:39.328 --> 00:02:44.036
And so we suffer from disappointments and frustrations.

00:02:44.116 --> 00:02:50.672
And the love that has to be nourishing and fulfilling

00:02:50.752 --> 00:02:54.752
becomes a thankless job.

00:02:56.884 --> 00:02:59.655
So, when it reflects in the human beings,

00:02:59.735 --> 00:03:05.170
it is the desire to be loved by everyone,

00:03:05.250 --> 00:03:09.710
not to love others.

00:03:09.790 --> 00:03:16.116
Everyone should love you, but
how far you love another is the point.

00:03:16.196 --> 00:03:19.124
Naturally everyone for oneself!

00:03:19.204 --> 00:03:23.507
So really nobody loves.

00:03:23.587 --> 00:03:26.829
But when it comes to real love

00:03:26.909 --> 00:03:32.406
then sacrifice, becomes a nature.

00:03:32.486 --> 00:03:37.548
You don’t call it a sacrifice, but you call it a privilege.

00:03:37.628 --> 00:03:41.885
We say it’s a privilege to give love.

00:03:41.965 --> 00:03:46.971
It’s a great chance that we can love.

00:03:47.051 --> 00:03:51.373
It’s our great fortune that we can love.

00:03:51.453 --> 00:03:57.235
It’s God’s blessings that we can love and give.

00:03:57.315 --> 00:04:02.343
So, the giving starts when you realise,

00:04:02.423 --> 00:04:06.496
not understand but realise the love,

00:04:06.576 --> 00:04:10.237
the power of love expressing .

00:04:10.317 --> 00:04:14.318
That’s the third power, which starts expressing .

00:04:14.398 --> 00:04:19.921
Because, after this, a person becomes active, kriyasheet.

00:04:20.001 --> 00:04:24.971
That’s how the action of

00:04:25.051 --> 00:04:29.080
achieving that state of giving love starts.

00:04:29.160 --> 00:04:33.881
To begin with we start activating in so many ways.

00:04:33.961 --> 00:04:39.971
As I said, we start expecting

00:04:40.051 --> 00:04:47.514
and thinking that we are loving others.

00:04:47.594 --> 00:04:50.971
We act for that.

00:04:51.051 --> 00:04:54.535
In that madness that others should love us,

00:04:54.615 --> 00:04:56.616
others should respect us,

00:04:56.696 --> 00:04:58.697
others should think we are great,

00:04:58.777 --> 00:05:00.890
they should recognise us

00:05:00.970 --> 00:05:06.036
we start loving something else which is not so important.

00:05:06.116 --> 00:05:10.661
So, we go on first to money,

00:05:10.741 --> 00:05:14.515
money becomes a very important point.

00:05:14.595 --> 00:05:19.484
We think that, if we have money, people will love us.

00:05:19.564 --> 00:05:26.201
We become very powerful as moneyed people, as rich people.

00:05:26.281 --> 00:05:28.971
So, we start accumulating money,

00:05:29.051 --> 00:05:36.074
we start loving the money.

00:05:36.154 --> 00:05:40.889
But money is not the Truth; we don’t love the Truth.

00:05:40.969 --> 00:05:43.395
When we start loving the money

00:05:43.475 --> 00:05:46.971
we start thinking about problems of money.

00:05:47.051 --> 00:05:54.081
Such people can become miserly to such an extent

00:05:54.161 --> 00:05:56.811
that even towards God they become miserly.

00:05:56.891 --> 00:05:58.708
They never have money actually,

00:05:58.788 --> 00:06:02.560
because if you cannot spend your money, you have no money.

00:06:02.640 --> 00:06:07.712
If it is not available what’s the
use of having all the money?

00:06:07.792 --> 00:06:10.962
That’s how they have problems

00:06:11.042 --> 00:06:17.246
because they love money and not the God Almighty.

00:06:17.326 --> 00:06:22.971
They’re worried about money but not about the Truth.

00:06:23.051 --> 00:06:28.109
Then with that they go to a second thing: is the power.

00:06:28.189 --> 00:06:32.838
They want to have the power; they want to become presidents,

00:06:32.918 --> 00:06:38.644
ministers and bureaucrats and all that.

00:06:38.724 --> 00:06:42.808
They want to have the power:
they think by having great power

00:06:42.888 --> 00:06:45.755
people will respect them and love them.

00:06:45.835 --> 00:06:51.161
But they get drowned in fear.

00:06:51.241 --> 00:06:55.488
What they get is fear. All the time they have fear.

00:06:55.568 --> 00:06:57.815
Also moneyed people have fear.

00:06:57.895 --> 00:07:03.800
That’s why in the Bible it is
said that: wages of sin is fear.

00:07:03.880 --> 00:07:09.069
What is sin? Sin is not to love the Truth.

00:07:09.149 --> 00:07:13.649
Is the sin. When you don’t love the Truth then it is sin.

00:07:13.729 --> 00:07:20.588
So, when you start getting worried about your positions…

00:07:20.668 --> 00:07:25.304
Like the president feels that he’ll lose his job,

00:07:25.384 --> 00:07:32.449
the vice president thinks that he’ll be sacked,

00:07:32.529 --> 00:07:37.971
the prime minister thinks he may not be elected,

00:07:38.052 --> 00:07:40.858
the bureaucrats think they will lose their jobs,

00:07:40.939 --> 00:07:43.052
they won’t get promotions or something,

00:07:43.132 --> 00:07:44.971
there will be problem.

00:07:45.051 --> 00:07:48.632
All these people are suffering from terrible sense of fear.

00:07:48.712 --> 00:07:51.451
They have no freedom of any kind.

00:07:51.531 --> 00:07:56.424
And in that category people just go down so much with fear,

00:07:56.504 --> 00:08:00.110
that even worse than people with money.

00:08:00.190 --> 00:08:03.191
Because once they are lost, they are lost.

00:08:03.271 --> 00:08:06.931
They can never revive. No chance.

00:08:07.011 --> 00:08:10.971
Once you lose the elections you
are lost, nobody is going to look at you.

00:08:11.051 --> 00:08:14.477
I have known people who have been at a very high position

00:08:14.557 --> 00:08:19.161
and once they lose that position nobody looks at them,

00:08:19.241 --> 00:08:20.971
they just walk like straight,

00:08:21.051 --> 00:08:25.052
otherwise there will be at least
hundred cars to receive them.

00:08:25.132 --> 00:08:29.052
And once they lose their jobs
there’s nobody even to look at them.

00:08:29.132 --> 00:08:31.632
They just walk like ordinary people.

00:08:31.712 --> 00:08:33.958
Even seeing all these things happening,

00:08:34.038 --> 00:08:41.111
this truth just coming before them so clearly,

00:08:41.191 --> 00:08:44.773
they do not keep to that truth,

00:08:44.853 --> 00:08:47.503
they do not realise that truth,

00:08:47.583 --> 00:08:53.240
they do not have that realisation within them.

00:08:53.320 --> 00:08:59.459
They understand for a while, and they go after that.

00:08:59.539 --> 00:09:01.578
Then when the person dies,

00:09:01.658 --> 00:09:07.204
they see a moneyed man, a rich man is forgotten,

00:09:07.284 --> 00:09:11.285
nobody is bothered about them, who was a rich man.

00:09:11.365 --> 00:09:13.100
On the contrary, the people,

00:09:13.180 --> 00:09:17.504
the prime ministers and all those
high-ranking people, when they die,

00:09:17.584 --> 00:09:22.065
immediately books start coming out about their private life:

00:09:22.145 --> 00:09:25.441
all the dirty things they did

00:09:25.521 --> 00:09:30.070
and all the horrible things they
did and what sort of life they led

00:09:30.150 --> 00:09:32.151
There’s no fragrance in their life,

00:09:32.231 --> 00:09:36.231
no idealism. Nothing.

00:09:37.357 --> 00:09:39.910
Because the responsibility

00:09:39.990 --> 00:09:42.803
that they have to the public

00:09:42.883 --> 00:09:46.784
and to themselves they have not understood it

00:09:46.864 --> 00:09:49.392
and they made a mess of their private life.

00:09:49.472 --> 00:09:56.423
That’s why this kind of a reaction comes after it.

00:09:56.503 --> 00:10:02.663
The other day I was reading an
interview with a very well-known actor.

00:10:02.743 --> 00:10:07.094
He’s a born realised fellow, I
know, but he’s gone down completely.

00:10:07.174 --> 00:10:09.801
He says, “I think, what’s the harm in drinking,

00:10:09.881 --> 00:10:11.652
what’s the harm in gambling,?

00:10:11.732 --> 00:10:14.599
what’s the harm in smoking?

00:10:14.679 --> 00:10:17.971
Because, after all, I’m going to die

00:10:18.051 --> 00:10:22.316
and then who is going to bother?

00:10:22.396 --> 00:10:26.285
Supposing, I get cancer, so
what? In any case I’m going to die.

00:10:26.365 --> 00:10:30.150
So why not enjoy these pleasures of life?”

00:10:30.230 --> 00:10:35.882
But what about death? You continue with it.

00:10:35.962 --> 00:10:40.126
Then all that you’ve been doing will come out,

00:10:40.206 --> 00:10:45.073
and people will not to like to have
your photograph in the household.

00:10:45.153 --> 00:10:48.671
Children will spit at you. What about that?

00:10:48.751 --> 00:10:53.219
Your life is not what it is today
for three, four years or ten years

00:10:53.299 --> 00:10:56.300
or fifteen years of your so-called success.

00:10:56.380 --> 00:11:03.098
But when you die all this craziness will disappear,

00:11:03.178 --> 00:11:06.788
and people will come out with truth about you.

00:11:06.868 --> 00:11:12.751
That is how this power to be popular finishes off.

00:11:14.017 --> 00:11:16.300
This cheap popularity,

00:11:16.380 --> 00:11:24.380
this cheap type of treatment towards yourself

00:11:26.067 --> 00:11:31.045
gives you a personality that will not be worshipped,

00:11:31.125 --> 00:11:33.671
that will not be accepted.

00:11:33.751 --> 00:11:36.274
Nobody will quote you as something great.

00:11:36.354 --> 00:11:38.355
For some time, it will continue,

00:11:38.435 --> 00:11:45.933
but in totality such a person has given nothing to humanity.

00:11:47.366 --> 00:11:50.669
That’s how the power of Saraswati works.

00:11:50.749 --> 00:11:54.247
People go into action

00:11:54.327 --> 00:12:02.820
for achieving the results of getting into power.

00:12:02.900 --> 00:12:08.751
But it should act to discover the truth.

00:12:10.856 --> 00:12:17.901
Saraswati should give you the leap to find out the truth.

00:12:17.981 --> 00:12:24.874
That, when you act in those funny places and streets,

00:12:24.954 --> 00:12:29.055
you discover this is not the path, we have missed it.

00:12:29.135 --> 00:12:32.761
The path is somewhere else. We’ve lost it.

00:12:32.841 --> 00:12:36.357
Let us find out the real path because this doesn’t give joy.

00:12:36.437 --> 00:12:38.524
This one can learn from others,

00:12:38.604 --> 00:12:43.626
from history, from so many other
things and from your own parents,

00:12:43.706 --> 00:12:48.954
from your society and from
yourself and from your children also.

00:12:49.034 --> 00:12:51.846
If you want to learn,

00:12:51.926 --> 00:12:55.408
that is the quality of Saraswati pujaris,

00:12:55.488 --> 00:13:00.253
that they take to gyana, they take to reality.

00:13:00.333 --> 00:13:03.464
Vedas, in the beginning of the Vedas,

00:13:03.544 --> 00:13:08.059
it’s said that: if by reading these four Vedas,

00:13:09.487 --> 00:13:13.260
if you do not get the veeda,

00:13:13.340 --> 00:13:19.111
veeda is the knowledge on your nerves, means Realisation,

00:13:19.191 --> 00:13:28.508
there is no use reading these Vedas.

00:13:28.588 --> 00:13:35.217
So, the Saraswati’s first thing is that through the reading,

00:13:35.297 --> 00:13:40.545
through the process of Saraswati’s manifestation,

00:13:40.625 --> 00:13:44.733
you must reach a point to
understand that this is a rat-race,

00:13:44.813 --> 00:13:46.467
and we have to get out of it.

00:13:46.547 --> 00:13:48.326
We have to step out.

00:13:48.406 --> 00:13:50.513
When that happens,

00:13:50.593 --> 00:13:53.478
then the Mahalakshmi Tattwa starts working in you,

00:13:53.558 --> 00:13:58.558
that is the third tattwa, which starts working.

00:14:03.526 --> 00:14:11.103
Mahalakshmi Tattwa then starts
expressing its love in its full extent

00:14:11.183 --> 00:14:15.408
through evolutionary process in human beings.

00:14:15.488 --> 00:14:19.691
He starts evolving simultaneously.

00:14:19.771 --> 00:14:23.545
He sees on both the sides what’s happening,

00:14:23.625 --> 00:14:31.563
like a witness and he uses his Mahalakshmi power.

00:14:31.643 --> 00:14:35.961
In the first part of the Mahalakshmi power

00:14:36.041 --> 00:14:43.486
he starts getting out of the
common rut of the family bondages

00:14:43.566 --> 00:14:51.283
and the other human bondages of power,

00:14:51.363 --> 00:14:55.083
money, lust

00:14:55.163 --> 00:14:59.913
and he starts moving on a higher plane.

00:15:00.966 --> 00:15:08.019
He gives us a new idea of popularity

00:15:08.099 --> 00:15:13.348
by establishing the Truth.

00:15:13.428 --> 00:15:15.630
Because through Mahalakshmi power

00:15:15.710 --> 00:15:21.256
you discover the Truth on your central nervous system

00:15:21.336 --> 00:15:32.336
and ultimately it is the light of an enlightened brain.

00:15:35.490 --> 00:15:41.448
When the Mahalakshmi power starts manifesting,

00:15:41.528 --> 00:15:45.630
one starts thinking of others.

00:15:45.710 --> 00:15:48.287
Not on material level,

00:15:48.367 --> 00:15:50.630
that materially people are suffering,

00:15:50.710 --> 00:15:55.807
“Now there are people in Ethiopia, who will
save? We must give them some food, this, that.

00:15:55.887 --> 00:16:01.509
” No! They go to the roots of the problems. Why?

00:16:01.589 --> 00:16:07.119
Or they don’t think there should be
equal distribution of money and wealth.

00:16:07.199 --> 00:16:09.262
No. This is superficial.

00:16:09.342 --> 00:16:16.342
Because wherever it is done people are not happy.

00:16:18.065 --> 00:16:21.970
They feel they have no freedom.

00:16:23.629 --> 00:16:27.266
Those people who have money are not happy

00:16:27.346 --> 00:16:31.371
because they have a demonic life.

00:16:31.451 --> 00:16:35.212
Where they are free they behave like devils.

00:16:35.292 --> 00:16:41.813
No sense of totality, no sense of collectivity.

00:16:41.893 --> 00:16:45.548
When they become like that,

00:16:47.819 --> 00:16:54.363
they even do not realise that they have become demonic.

00:16:54.443 --> 00:17:00.443
Everything becomes like a big martyrdom.

00:17:01.710 --> 00:17:09.123
They fight for lands, they fight
for nations, they fight for rights.

00:17:09.203 --> 00:17:11.968
And they do all kinds of horrible things.

00:17:12.048 --> 00:17:19.309
Start destroying people, human beings.

00:17:19.389 --> 00:17:24.949
All the turmoil of today is the effect of

00:17:25.029 --> 00:17:28.324
mostly in the West,

00:17:28.404 --> 00:17:31.513
and also all the Arabic countries,

00:17:31.593 --> 00:17:36.746
I would say – is of the right side.

00:17:36.826 --> 00:17:42.827
And in the East, it is of the left side - the turmoils.

00:17:42.907 --> 00:17:47.293
It’s very surprising that

00:17:47.373 --> 00:17:51.469
it’s very contrasting also. It’s a funny dilemma for Me,

00:17:51.549 --> 00:17:53.899
I can’t understand it sometimes

00:17:53.979 --> 00:17:59.292
that where they are so particular about the chastity,

00:18:03.710 --> 00:18:10.389
they become when they are so much
worried about chastity and everything,

